<h3>lerp()</h3>

``` js
Zdog.lerp( a, b, alpha )
```

<p>Linear interpolation between values <code>a</code> and <code>b</code> given a percent decimal <code>alpha</code>.</p>

``` js
// 75% of the way between 20 and 40
Zdog.lerp( 20, 40, 0.75 );
// => 35
```

